channel.title: Anyone want a free month of a domain?
channel.description: Well about 4-5 days ago I bought a business package from hostgator. Turns out I didnt need it so I cancelled it. They told me it will be deleted after the next cycle so there is about 25 days left. If you want it just lemme know and i'll hand over the domain name + cpanel login.
